Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,brume0425僅分享於伊莉論壇/動畫下載區(免空)請勿任意轉載
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:06.89,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,Darling好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:12.71,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,今後我打算以結婚為前提和妳交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:13.71,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:17.86,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,Darling~ ~ ~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:27.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,結‧‧‧結婚嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:32.54,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,為了能隨時隨地保護主公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:35.08,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,必須做好劍的保養
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:38.34,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,吶~珊卓雷雅 我們來玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.36,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,別胡鬧 帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:41.59,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我正在保養劍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:43.75,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:44.93,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,都說別鬧了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.19,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,好 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.28,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,大家 吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.59,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,吶~主人 來玩遊戲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:00.57,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮 吃完飯再說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:02.40,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.08,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,好香!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:11.12,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,今天吃什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:15.42,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:48.53,標題,btume045,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}「史萊姆的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.28,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,剛才那究竟是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.24,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那是史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.95,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,史萊姆˙那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.53,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,還有很多人類社會無法認知的的他種族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.04,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,史萊姆也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.83,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不過 請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:21.51,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,就由我來保護主公!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.71,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,以吾之利劍起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:24.97,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,雖然是仿真刀‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:29.59,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,絕不會讓史萊姆這種低等動物傷害到主公的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,嗯‧‧‧謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.36,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,吶咦~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,來玩遊戲吧~一起玩嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.16,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,現在不是玩鬧的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.40,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.48,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,妳在笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.26,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,大家一起玩很開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:44.97,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼 現在沒空跟妳玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:45.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮真的是相當沉迷於遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.19,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,快點趴下!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.20,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,離主公遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:04:00.64,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,什‧‧‧居然沒有作用?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:04.83,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,所謂史萊姆不是在RPG裡最低級的雜碎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.21,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,賽蕾雅的知識有偏斜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.22,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,賽蕾雅 沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:19.10,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,是‧‧‧還好‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.68,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,沒想到史萊姆竟然這麼強‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.96,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,身上都黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.74,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,主公 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.13,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.99,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我‧‧‧我稍微去沖一下澡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.03,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮也要小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:37.74,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這孩子‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.14,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,沒想到會出現史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.31,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,怎麼感覺好魔幻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.05,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.13,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,要聯絡一下墨須小姐嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.71,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,主公‧‧‧那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.14,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.25,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.90,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧嗯 我沒事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.48,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,是..是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:08.92,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那樣的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.44,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:12.78,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.20,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.97,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,賽蕾雅 妳幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.67,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.30,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我並沒有不純的動機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.01,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,說不定史萊姆還會襲擊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.84,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,所以‧‧‧不能讓主公一個人‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.97,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,迫不得已! 是迫不得已啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.04,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那樣的話 穿上衣服不是也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.18,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那是‧‧‧哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.55,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,因為黏在身上的史萊姆黏液弄不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.49,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,所以想讓主公幫忙洗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.32,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,給您添麻煩了 非常抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.15,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不會 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:01.54,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳也是為了保護我才會弄髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.94,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但妳的手搆不到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.62,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳平常都不洗嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.34,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,有再洗! 用把柄很長的刷子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.29,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,因為今天格外的髒‧‧‧所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.34,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧主公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:21.10,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那裡是‧‧‧屁股附近就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.75,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那裡是..這個那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.75,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,比較敏感的部位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.92,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,對不起  說的也是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.18,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,畢竟是屁股附近 肯定會有敏感部位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.53,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,別那麼大聲‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.03,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那麼 洗其他的地方‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.54,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不對!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.94,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,抱歉 我太慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.42,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,總之不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:55.26,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,一開始到浴池裡不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:01.59,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不過為什麼史萊姆會襲擊我們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.53,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.02,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,水?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:08.52,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我猜它可能是要吸取水分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.54,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,最初是鍋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.77,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,接著是洗臉盆的水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.36,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,雖然只是推測
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:17.15,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,它可能有尋求水的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.78,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,水‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.16,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧泡澡也很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.26,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,史萊姆 是什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.01,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那不是劍啊‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.19,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,賽蕾雅 妳不要緊吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等一下‧‧‧暫停!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.24,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,就算吃了我也得不到營養喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:57.53,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,再說 打男人什麼的也不會有這種需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.62,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,什‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.36,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,女孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.48,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 是這種種族嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.20,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳‧‧‧妳要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.78,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等一下! 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.56,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,還沒做好心理準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:50.33,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那個‧‧‧等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:54.06,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,為什麼突然幫我洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.03,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:02.79,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳有在聽我說話嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:05.79,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,語言不通嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.83,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,為什麼突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:12.23,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,彷彿就像我剛才幫賽蕾雅洗身體一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.21,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,該不會?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:19.73,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這孩子剛剛做的這些 是在模仿嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.24,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,想要藉著模仿進行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.99,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,說不定不是什麼危險生物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.16,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,抓不住‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.72,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,出不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.36,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,呼吸要‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.50,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,拜託妳 史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.92,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,想要交流的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:46.14,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,先讀懂我的想法!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.31,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,果然無法溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.42,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,呼‧‧‧呼吸要‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.09,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不行了 意識要‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:59.96,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是 既然如此 只能賭一把了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.66,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,死‧‧‧還以為死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.32,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,給我暫時先安分待在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:24.98,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,用稀釋打敗了史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:27.22,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,真讓人佩服 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,Darling 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.97,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,也只是碰運氣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:38.48,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,搞不好的話讓她吸收更多水份 變成巨大怪獸也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:42.36,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不過史萊姆能變成人形 真的嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.61,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,人形?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.47,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,而且胸部很大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:47.43,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.91,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧不是 那個這個. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.95,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不過說到人形史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.83,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,哎 很罕見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.95,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,從沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.52,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,果然還是要跟墨須小姐報告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.45,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,她能認真處理嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:08.22,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,畢竟那個人太隨意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:11.51,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,把她丟在浴室不管沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.89,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這個‧‧‧會怎樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:15.21,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,應該不會在逃跑‧‧‧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:30.06,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔~物~娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.94,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我的馬克杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.77,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那跟Darling可是一對的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.76,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這‧‧‧這是什麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.93,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我的劍怎麼黏黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.25,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這個可惡的史萊姆!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.69,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,好了 好了 好了‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.52,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,好了 好了 別太生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:03.69,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇又不是故意做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.69,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.64,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,因為是史萊姆所以叫蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.20,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,是帕皮取的名子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.75,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.99,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,嗯~蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.41,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,說話了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.34,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,看來很擅長模仿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:21.41,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是也不能讓她一直這副打扮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.87,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,可是那樣黏黏糊糊的身體不能穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.47,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,雨衣!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.74,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不會滲水進去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.91,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,弄濕也不會變透明 不錯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.27,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不愧是Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.61,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇~好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.21,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.78,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,感覺反而變得更色情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:54.20,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,說起來我記得她應該更大一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.55,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,為什麼變小了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.00,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,從浴池裡逃出來的時後排出一些水份了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.24,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.28,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,或許‧‧‧那才是她真正的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.75,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮 我是帕皮喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.75,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,帕比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.72,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是Darling 你打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.38,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:10.01,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那孩子恐怕不是通過正規途徑來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.17,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,可能是混在貨物中來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.23,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,或著是被什麼人帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.28,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那不是非法入境嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:20.52,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,應該讓墨須小姐來接管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.78,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,都不知道她從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.95,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,沒辦法遣返吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:30.78,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,恐怕會安置在保護觀察科 或者被監禁也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.28,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,監禁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.53,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,儘管怎麼說 這也太‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.53,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,監禁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.12,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是這樣下去主公也會受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:45.92,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,主公 我認為還是應該盡快交給墨須小姐處理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:50.42,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,就連我們到現在還會和人類社會發生一些摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:54.68,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我不認為那個史萊姆可以跨越這些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.67,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,說不定哪天就會鑄下大錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:03.91,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,到那之後我們構築的一切都白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.52,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等一下! 帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.70,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳要把史萊姆帶去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.45,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等等 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.96,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳要去哪裡? 帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.93,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不要亂動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.18,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇~ ~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.21,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,咦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.20,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧? 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.69,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,好厲害 完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:54.19,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這裡有個有事的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.75,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不過妳為什麼突然亂動呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:03.55,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我猜她大概害怕河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.45,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,從她會融入浴池來看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:09.43,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,吸入大量的水份大概就會融化死掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:13.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,是這樣啊 對不起 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,在對那孩子道歉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.91,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,為什麼要逃跑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:20.32,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我不是說過沒有我一起不能出去外面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:23.94,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,而且‧‧‧還帶著蘇‧‧‧一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:27.46,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,因為你們想把蘇抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.28,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,明明什麼壞事都沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.70,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,沒做過什麼壞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.17,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我可是差點就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.86,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,那不是一直都有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.97,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是‧‧‧他種族間交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:43.37,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,總之 蘇由帕皮來保護!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.87,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,保護‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.37,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,保護?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.67,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,喂~鳥姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.57,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我們在玩水槍大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:58.26,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,鳥姐姐也一起來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.87,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮 妳認識嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:04.57,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,鳥姊姊經常和我們一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.35,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,哦 妳是之前那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.97,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,咦? 經常?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:10.27,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,嗯~昨天也一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:14.41,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮 妳一個人擅自偷跑出去玩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.74,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是帕皮為什麼這麼受歡迎‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.24,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,快跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.84,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,還真敢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.49,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,別跑你們這些‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:26.58,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.13,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.46,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這才是目標嗎? 色小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:39.43,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,話說回來 帕皮意外的會照顧人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.89,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,也說要保護蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.97,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,說不定是母性本能比較強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.24,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不要~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.48,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,等等‧‧‧快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.05,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,喂喂 你‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.25,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:15.33,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,原來如此 吸收適當的水份就會變大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.13,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不過變大是想要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.93,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,在模仿帕皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:28.57,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,下一個換我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.25,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不對 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.18,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,拜託讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.61,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,怎‧‧‧怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.54,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,鼻子進水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.81,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.45,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,追!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.54,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:03.01,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,主公 我認為還是盡快交給墨須小姐來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:08.68,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是那孩子只是樂在其中而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.95,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 本大爺的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:24.26,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,說到車還是美國車好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:26.61,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這車稍微不妙的說‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.12,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不妙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.33,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.22,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,沒事吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.24,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇救了那個女孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:50.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,是用自己的身體吸收的車子的衝擊力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.24,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,史萊姆姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是蘇妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,咦! 被撞到牆壁上身體不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:15.96,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇 ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:22.57,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:29.72,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮的手沒辦法好好抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:38.08,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,如果掉進河裡 蘇會‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:40.33,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.99,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.12,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.11,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.63,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.64,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.12,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.65,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.15,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.43,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇~蘇~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:29.16,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,沒事 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.15,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.17,Default-b,btume045,0,0,0,,沒事 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:37.66,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,咦 暫時要把她留在家照顧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.79,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不用那麼驚訝‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.22,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,不用擔心也沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.17,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,她不是一個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.79,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,只是有點缺乏常識而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:52.68,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,可是 主公要是發生什麼事‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:56.93,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,明明什都沒做就要通報的事我做不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:21:01.60,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,今後認真教她些常識之類的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.73,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,可是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:03.75,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,但是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:05.19,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,沒問題的!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.48,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,把她當孩子看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.19,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.86,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:13.53,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,父親  母親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.08,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,真是的 既然這麼說那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.04,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我‧‧‧我在想什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:24.39,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,作為侍奉主公之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.29,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,這不切實際妄想‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.98,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,妳們兩個 不要被墨須小姐發現了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:30.80,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.36,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,真的懂了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.48,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,哦  對了 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.30,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,咦 什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:38.18,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我已經到家了 先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.40,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,我回來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.59,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,剛才墨須小姐來家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.29,Default,btume045,0,0,0,,你們回來的時候小心別被發現..
